entries.journal_entry_description: Qakkee believes he's the greatest hunter in the Galaxy. Prove that you are his equal!
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Find 10 cannibal Dewbacks, kill them and remove their jaws as evidence for Qakkee.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Bring the Dewback jaws back to Qakkee and, if you feel like it, laugh at him.
